        OUR_TROOPS_AT_THE_STRONGHOLD_IN_WILL_BE_2                             = 11258,  -- Our troops at the stronghold in [North Gustaberg/Grauberg/Pashhow Marshlands/Rolanberry Fields] will be informed of your coming. Luck ride with you!
        OUR_TROOPS_AT_THE_STRONGHOLD_IN_WILL_BE_3                             = 11259,  -- Our troops at the stronghold in [West Sarutabaruta/Fort Karugo-Narugo/Meriphataud Mountains/Sauromugue Champaign] will be informed of your coming. Luck ride with you!
        I_M_SORRY_BUT_WE_DON_T_PUT                                            = 11260,  -- I'm sorry, but we don't put our chocobos in the hands of people with %. We wouldn't want our feathered friends dying from fright now, would we?
        MY_FRIENDS_AND_I_PUT_TOGTHER_A_BASTOKAN                               = 11261,  -- My friends and I put togther a Bastokan Time Capsule! I'm going to have my father bury it somewhere deep beneath North Gustaberg.
        HAVE_YOU_HEARD_OF_MY_FATHER_HE_S                                      = 11262,  -- Have you heard of my father? He's a great soldier, you know! I want him to bury it somewhere near Drachenfall so that it's easy to find.
        WHAT_YOU_THINK_IF_THE_SPOT_IS_TOO                                     = 11263,  -- What? You think if the spot is too obvious the capsule might be found by Goblins!?
        WELL_I_CAN_T_LET_ANY_BEASTMEN_GET                                     = 11264,  -- Well, I can't let any beastmen get their grubby paws on it! We're already looking forward to reading our letters... What do you think we should do?
        WHAT_ADVICE_WILL_YOU_GIVE_OFFA_BURY_IT                                = 11265,  -- What advice will you give Offa? Bury it somewhere in the city. Conceal the burial spot with a rock.
        DO_YOU_REALLY_WANT_TO_ADVISE_OFFA_TO                                  = 11266,  -- Do you really want to advise Offa to [bury it in the city/conceal it with a rock]? Yes, it's the only way. No, on second thought...
        THAT_SETTLES_IT_I_LL_HAVE_MY_FATHER                                   = 11267,  -- That settles it! I'll have my father bury it within the city walls. Good thinking!
        THAT_SETTLES_IT_I_LL_HAVE_MY_FATHER_2                                 = 11268,  -- That settles it! I'll have my father cover up the burial spot with a rock. You're a genius!
        OF_COURSE_I_LL_JUST_HAVE_MY_FATHER                                    = 11269,  -- Of course! I'll just have my father bury it here in the city. Why didn't I think of that?
        OF_COURSE_I_LL_JUST_HAVE_MY_FATHER_2                                  = 11270,  -- Of course! I'll just have my father cover up the burial spot with a rock! Why didn't I think of that?
        I_CAN_T_EVEN_SLEEP_AT_NIGHT_WHEN                                      = 11271,  -- I can't even sleep at night when I start thinking about the beastmen attacking the city... How long is it going to be like this?
        HUH_YOU_THINK_WE_MIGHT_FORGET_WHERE_WE                                = 11272,  -- Huh? You think we might forget where we buried the capsule? Hmmm...maybe we should bury it somewhere near the Drachenfall after all.
        I_WAS_THINKING_THE_SAME_THING_OH_WELL                                 = 11273,  -- I was thinking the same thing. Oh well, I'll just have my father rebury it in a better spot. We could even go with your other idea and have him cover it up with a rock to keep away all the Goblins.
        I_SURE_DO_FEEL_A_LOT_BETTER_KNOWING                                   = 11274,  -- I sure do feel a lot better, knowing our capsule's resting place is hidden under a rock. Thank you so much for your advice!
        HM_YOU_WANT_TO_BURY_THIS_IN_THE                                       = 11275,  -- Hm? You want to bury this in the time capsule too?
        I_THINK_YOU_MAY_BE_ON_TO_SOMETHING                                    = 11276,  -- I think you may be on to something! Even if some goblins do find it, they'll be so busy with these bones that they won't even notice the letters!
        ALL_RIGHT_I_LL_HAVE_MY_FATHER_REBURY                                  = 11277,  -- All right! I'll have my father rebury it right away.
        I_HAD_TOTALLY_FORGOTTEN_HOW_CRAZY_GOBLINS_ARE                         = 11278,  -- I had totally forgotten how crazy goblins are for fish bones. Thanks again for the great advice!
        WHAT_S_THAT_YOU_WANT_TO_REBURY_THE                                    = 11279,  -- What's that? You want to rebury the capsule...again? I appreciate your concern, but it should be just fine where it is.
        A_WHAT_A_FALSE_BOTTOM_IN_THE_BOX                                      = 11280,  -- A what? A false bottom? In the box? Now that could be just the ticket...There's no way any goblins would be able to find the letters then.
        ALL_RIGHT_BUT_THIS_IS_THE_LAST_TIME                                   = 11281,  -- All right, but this is the last time...seriously. My father is getting sick of digging.
