        TOO_BAD_BUT_WHILE_YOU_WERE_OFF_PICKIN                                 = 11379,  -- Too bad, %, but while you were off pickin' your nose, some other volunteers signed up in your place. Maybe next time you should learn to move your feet instead of flappin' your gums!
        HEY_WAIT_YOU_AIN_T_GOT_NO_OP                                          = 11380,  -- Hey, wait! You ain't got no Op Credits! I like your enthusiasm, %, but rules are rules. I'll see you back here tomorrow.
        WHAT_IN_ATOMOS_S_NAME_ARE_YOU_DOIN                                    = 11381,  -- What in Atomos's name are you doin' here? Aren't you supposed to be on duty? Or...
