        DELIVER_THEM_WHERE_YOU_ASK_YOU_VE_SEEN                                = 11545,  -- Deliver them where, you ask? You've seen the watchtowers out in Gustaberg, right? There's one called Eduard and it's manned by a Centurion Gebhardt.
