        I_AM_AFRAID_THAT_THERE_ARE_NO_UNIONS                                  = 11845,  -- I am afraid that there are no unions in need of your services at this time.
        HMPH_I_SEE_THAT_YOU_HAVE_NO_ALLIED                                    = 11846,  -- Hmph. I see that you have no Allied Tags in your possession. Our unions cannot very well accept any straggler who walks in off the streets. Come back after you've proved yourself in the war effort, and we shall talk again.
