        DUE_TO_THE_STRAIN_THE_WAR_HAS_PUT                                     = 11857,  -- Due to the strain the war has put on our supply levels, the Allied War Council has recommended that we hire hundreds of new initiates to help with the synthesis of new items. However, with the guildmasters all working overtime manufacturing goods, we don't have enough manpower to aid us in the training of the new recruits.
