        WOULD_YOU_LEND_A_HAND_OF_COURSE_I                                     = 11859,  -- Would you lend a hand? Of course! I'm sorry. My hands are tied.
        THAT_IS_UNFORTUNATE_THERE_ARE_MEN_AND_WOMEN                           = 11860,  -- That is unfortunate. There are men and women dying on the frontlines because they don't have the supplies they need to drive back the beastman hordes. If you are just going to look the other way, then so be it...
