        YOU_ARE_CURRENTLY_IN_POSSESSION_OF_THE_MOST_2                         = 12169,  -- You are currently in possession of the most prestigious Campaign medal we have to offer. The Republic of Bastok has the utmost faith in you, and shall support you in any endeavor you choose to undertake.
