        HM_BUSINESS_WITH_NICOLAUS_OF_THE_MYTHRIL_MUSKETEERS                   = 12181,  -- Hm? Business with Nicolaus of the Mythril Musketeers, you say?
        WELL_IF_IT_ISN_T_HOW_MAY_I                                            = 12182,  -- Well, if it isn't %. How may I be of service to you today?
        YOU_WISHED_TO_SEE_ME_ABOUT_SOMETHING                                  = 12183,  -- You wished to see me about something?
        IT_S_ALRIGHT_GENTLE_TIGER_PLEASE_LEAVE_US                             = 12184,  -- It's alright, Gentle Tiger. Please, leave us.
        HMMM_ERLENE                                                           = 12185,  -- Hmmm... Erlene...
        SO_PROFESSOR_SCHULTZ_HAS_GONE_AND_DISAPPEARED_UNANNOUNCED             = 12186,  -- So Professor Schultz has gone and disappeared unannounced yet again, has he?
        HE_HAS_ALWAYS_BEEN_QUITE_THE_ENTHUSIAST_FOR                           = 12187,  -- He has always been quite the enthusiast for trying out new techniques in private. Why, I still recall one of his previous disappearing acts. One moment he was standing right before my eyes and the next he was gone, after calling forth one of those storms of his.
        THE_MARCH_OF_TIME_MUST_HAVE_BEEN_SOMEHOW                              = 12188,  -- The march of time must have been somehow different in...well, wherever he was.
        HE_CLAIMS_HE_INTENDED_TO_BE_GONE_FOR                                  = 12189,  -- He claims he intended to be gone for only a short while. And yet some three weeks passed with no sign of his return. Caused quite the ruckus among the people here, it did.
        AS_ERLENE_PROPERLY_INFORMED_YOU_IN_THE_END                            = 12190,  -- As Erlene properly informed you, in the end it was I who stumbled upon the professor.
        I_SIMPLY_VISITED_HIS_RESIDENCE_TO_SEARCH_FOR                          = 12191,  -- I simply visited his residence to search for some clue as to his whereabouts.
        IT_WAS_THEN_THAT_I_SAW_THE_STORM                                      = 12192,  -- It was then that I saw the storm formulation posted out on the wall. And I became convinced that he had never even left the comfort of his own quarters.
        I_PROCEEDED_TO_CALL_OUT_HIS_NAME_NOT                                  = 12193,  -- I proceeded to call out his name, not hiding my agitation.
        AND_SURE_ENOUGH_THE_GOOD_PROFESSOR_MATERIALIZED_RIGHT                 = 12194,  -- And sure enough, the good professor materialized right there, in quiet contemplation before his chessboard.
        DID_ERLENE_HAPPEN_TO_MENTION_ANYTHING_ELSE_IN                         = 12195,  -- Did Erlene happen to mention anything else in regards to Professor Schultz?
        RECONNAISSANCE_EH_SO_THEN_HE_SEEKS_TO_GATHER                          = 12196,  -- Reconnaissance, eh? So then, he seeks to gather intelligence on the Beastman Confederate's movements.
        IT_IS_NO_DOUBT_THE_QUADAV_SHIELDWARRIORS_THAT                         = 12197,  -- It is no doubt the Quadav Shieldwarriors that have stirred his concern.
        IN_WHICH_CASE_IT_IS_MOST_PROBABLE_THAT                                = 12198,  -- In which case, it is most probable that he has headed for the Derfland Front.
        THAT_FRONT_EXTENDS_NORTHEAST_FROM_PASHHOW_MARSHLANDS_TO               = 12199,  -- That front extends northeast from Pashhow Marshlands to the Rolanberry Fields, and then farther north still to Vunkerl Inlet.
        BUT_THAT_IS_JUST_MY_BEST_GUESS_USING                                  = 12200,  -- But that is just my best guess... Using his art to conceal himself when he seeks privacy is one thing, but to be surrounded by enemies deep within hostile territory... That is truly a matter for grave concern.
        PERHAPS_IT_WOULD_BE_PRUDENT_TO_GO_AND                                 = 12201,  -- Perhaps it would be prudent to go and search for one of the professor's storms. Under the strictest of caution, naturally.
        HAS_THE_PROFESSOR_BEEN_LOCATED                                        = 12202,  -- Has the professor been located?
        WHAT_WAS_THAT_ABOUT_ROLANBERRY_AND_PASHHOW                            = 12203,  -- What was that about Rolanberry...? And Pashhow...?
        OH_WHAT_EVER_SHALL_I_DO_THE_DEADLINE                                  = 12204,  -- Oh, what ever shall I do... The deadline for my discourse draws near and I have yet to even gather the proper materials.
        GREETINGS_MAY_I_HELP_YOU_AH_A_PUPIL                                   = 12205,  -- Greetings. May I help you? Ah, a pupil of the Schultz school, I see.
        IN_WHICH_CASE_MAY_I_BE_SO_BOLD                                        = 12206,  -- In which case, may I be so bold as to inquire why you are dressed in such a manner? You would do well to consider the reputation of your school and fellow students before donning such garb in public.
        ACTUALLY                                                              = 12207,  -- Actually...
        WOULD_YOU_PERHAPS_BE_INTERESTED_IN_OBTAINING_SOME                     = 12208,  -- Would you perhaps be interested in obtaining some appropriate attire for yourself? It just so happens that I have quite some influence in such matters.
        I_REGRET_HOWEVER_THAT_I_CANNOT_OFFER_UP                               = 12209,  -- I regret, however, that I cannot offer up my services entirely free of charge. I'm sure in the course of your studies you've become familiar with the "Give and Take" school of economics.
        IT_IS_DECIDED_THEN_I_SHALL_PROCURE_THE                                = 12210,  -- It is decided, then. I shall procure the garments for you. In return, I would ask that you assist me with my current assignment.
        I_SAY_ASSIGNMENT_BUT_I_ASSURE_YOU_IT                                  = 12211,  -- I say assignment, but I assure you it is no significant charge. Simply one of those trivial and menial tasks which form the underpinnings of our beloved scholasticism.
        IT_S_JUST_THAT_GIVEN_THE_EVER_WORSENING                               = 12212,  -- It's just that given the ever-worsening state of affairs with the ongoing war and all, this assignment has become considerably more difficult than when the senior pupils were required to complete it.
        NO_NO_IT_WOULDN_T_BE_CHEATING_I                                       = 12213,  -- No, no. It wouldn't be cheating, I assure you. There are no rules governing methods of acquisition.
        IT_IS_JUST_AS_THE_OLD_TEXTS_TEACH                                     = 12214,  -- It is just as the old texts teach us, and as the professor always says. One hundred victories in as many battles does not a sage make. He who gains victory without confrontation is the true sage. To obtain one's objective through minimum effort is most sublime!
        IT_SOUNDS_LIKE_A_REASONABLE_ENOUGH_OFFER_TO                           = 12215,  -- It sounds like a reasonable enough offer to me. So what do you say?
        WHAT_WILL_YOU_DO_ACCEPT_THE_OFFER_DECLINE                             = 12216,  -- What will you do? Accept the offer. Decline the offer.
        I_SEE_THAT_IS_MOST_UNFORTUNATE_I_SUPPOSE                              = 12217,  -- I see. That is most...unfortunate. I suppose I will have to do it myself after all.
        OH_DID_SOMEBODY_HAVE_A_CHANGE_OF_HEART                                = 12218,  -- Oh! Did somebody have a change of heart? Have you given some further consideration to my offer?
        MOST_DELIGHTFUL_PLEASE_WAIT_HERE_JUST_A_MOMENT                        = 12219,  -- Most delightful! Please, wait here. Just a moment!
        PANT_PANT_HERE_WE_ARE_THEN_NOW_IF                                     = 12220,  -- <Pant, pant>... Here we are, then. Now, if you would be so kind as to select one of the following.
        WHICH_ITEM_ARE_YOU_INTERESTED_IN_GIVE_ME                              = 12221,  -- Which item are you interested in? %. %. %. Give me some time to mull it over.
        AHHH_CLASSIC_IN_THAT_CASE_I_MUST_ASK                                  = 12222,  -- Ahhh, %. Classic! In that case, I must ask this of you. Listen carefully.
        I_WILL_REQUIRE_YOU_TO_OBTAIN_AND_BRING                                = 12223,  -- I will require you to obtain and bring me % and... Oh yes! %. That should do it.
        ARE_YOU_SURE_IT_IS_THAT_YOU_WOULD                                     = 12224,  -- Are you sure it is % that you would like?
        ARE_YOU_SUREH_BEYOND_A_DOUBT_ON_SECOND                                = 12225,  -- Are you sureH Beyond a doubt. On second thought...
        NO_NEED_TO_WORRY_I_SHALL_PRODUCE_THE                                  = 12226,  -- No need to worry. I shall produce the attire, as per our agreement. You just see to getting those items we talked about.
        IT_WAS_YOU_WERE_AFTER_CORRECT                                         = 12227,  -- It was % you were after, correct?
        TO_COMPLETE_MY_ASSIGNMENT_I_WILL_NEED_AND                             = 12228,  -- To complete my assignment I will need % and %. Deliver those to me and that new garment is as good as yours!
        I_LL_GET_MY_HANDS_ON_WHILE_YOU                                        = 12229,  -- I'll get my hands on % while you are busying yourself rounding up those items. Go along, now. We both have some work to do.
        PERFECT_THIS_IS_IT_WITH_THIS_MY_ASSIGNMENT                            = 12230,  -- Perfect! This is it! With this, my assignment should pose no difficulty at all. Thank you, %!
        I_BELIEVE_THIS_IS_YOURS_THEN_HERE_IS                                  = 12231,  -- I believe this is yours, then. Here is %, as promised.
