        NO_UNAUTHORIZED_PERSONNEL_WILL_BE_PERMITTED_ENTRANCE_TO               = 12473,  -- No unauthorized personnel will be permitted entrance to the Metalworks.
        ESPECIALLY_NOT_AFTER_THE_BEATING_MY_PAY_TOOK                          = 12474,  -- Especially not after the beating my pay took the last time...hm?
        WE_HAVE_AN_ASSAILANT_S_UNKNOWN_METHOD_OF                              = 12475,  -- We have an assailant's unknown method of entry, and a victim slain in the dark...
        PERHAPS_THE_CHIEF_ENGINEER_COULD_CONSTRUCT_A_MACHINE                  = 12476,  -- Perhaps the Chief Engineer could construct a machine to calculate the possible vectors and points of--
        OH_I_M_AWFULLY_SORRY_I_VE_BEEN                                        = 12477,  -- Oh, I'm awfully sorry! I've been so focused on the mystery behind Senator Werner's assassination...
        YOU_SEE_I_HAPPENED_TO_BE_EAVESDRO_ER                                  = 12478,  -- You see, I happened to be eavesdro--er, I happened to overhear a conversation between some Mythril Musketeers...
        PROGRESS_REPORT                                                       = 12479,  -- Progress report.
        NOTHING_NEW_I_VE_DISCOVERED_NO_RECALCITRANT_WITNESSES                 = 12480,  -- Nothing new. I've discovered no recalcitrant witnesses, no conflicting evidence on the senator's movements...
        YOU_SPOKE_AGAIN_WITH_THE_GUARD_WHO_DISCOVERED                         = 12481,  -- You spoke again with the guard who discovered the body?
        THE_DETAILS_OF_HIS_REPORT_REMAIN_UNCHANGED                            = 12482,  -- The details of his report remain unchanged.
        HE_INSISTS_THAT_THIS_ROOM_HAD_BEEN_LOCKED                             = 12483,  -- He insists that this room had been locked since the morning, and was empty when he checked inside during his patrol--moments before the senator entered.
        THE_GUARD_YOU_SPEAK_OF_IS_HONEST_TO                                   = 12484,  -- The guard you speak of is honest to a fault. We have no reason to doubt his testimony.
        THEN_WE_CAN_ASSUME_THE_CRIME_SCENE_WAS                                = 12485,  -- Then we can assume the crime scene was unviolated at the time the body was discovered?
        HOW_IN_ALTANA_S_NAME_DID_THIS_MURDEROUS                               = 12486,  -- How in Altana's name did this murderous wraith slip in and out unnoticed...?
        THERE_S_ONE_OTHER_THING_THAT_SEEMS_OUT                                = 12487,  -- There's one other thing that seems out of place here.
        OUT_WITH_IT_NICOLAUS                                                  = 12488,  -- Out with it, Nicolaus.
        IT_GOES_BACK_TO_THE_REPORT_FROM_THE                                   = 12489,  -- It goes back to the report from the first guard...
        HE_STATED_THE_FOLLOWING                                               = 12490,  -- He stated the following:
        I_HEARD_THE_SENATOR_S_CRY_AND_RAN                                     = 12491,  -- I heard the senator's cry, and ran to investigate. I was obliged to break the door open in order to enter the room.
        HE_WENT_ON_TO_MENTION_PITCH_BLACKNESS_WHEN                            = 12492,  -- He went on to mention pitch blackness when he described the situation within.
        WHY_DIDN_T_THE_SENATOR_LIGHT_THE_LANTERN                              = 12493,  -- Why didn't the senator light the lantern?
        ID_12494                                                              = 12494,  -- ...!
        IS_IT_POSSIBLE_HE_WAS_ATTACKED_BEFORE_HE                              = 12495,  -- Is it possible he was attacked before he had the chance?
        IF_THAT_WERE_TRUE_THEN_THE_BODY_WOULD                                 = 12496,  -- If that were true, then the body would have been found over here, where the tools for lighting the lantern are located.
        HOWEVER_IT_APPEARS_THAT_THE_SENATOR_WALKED_INTO                       = 12497,  -- However, it appears that the senator walked into the center of the room, without touching those tools at all.
        WHY_WOULD_HE_HAVE_GONE_SO_FAR_INTO                                    = 12498,  -- Why would he have gone so far into the room without a light by which to see?
        THAT_IS_UNUSUAL_THERE_WERE_NO_SIGNS_THAT                              = 12499,  -- That is unusual. There were no signs that the body was moved, either. We can only assume that he blundered through the dark of his own accord.
        PERHAPS_SENATOR_WERNER_WAS_FLEEING_FROM_HIS_ATTACKER                  = 12500,  -- Perhaps Senator Werner was fleeing from his attacker before he was stabbed...although the guard reported only a single cry.
        ONE_PRESUMES_HE_CRIED_OUT_THE_MOMENT_HIS                              = 12501,  -- One presumes he cried out the moment his assailant plunged home the dagger.
        A_MURDEROUS_WRAITH_AND_A_VICTIM_SLAIN_IN                              = 12502,  -- A murderous wraith, and a victim slain in the dark...
        WHAT_DO_YOU_MAKE_OF_THIS_NICOLAUS                                     = 12503,  -- What do you make of this, Nicolaus?
        I_HONESTLY_COULDN_T_SAY_I_HAVE_SEVERAL                                = 12504,  -- I honestly couldn't say. I have several theories, but I need more information to make a final judgment...
        I_USED_TO_STUDY_IN_THE_SAME_CLASSES                                   = 12505,  -- I used to study in the same classes as Mythril Musketeer Nicolaus.
        EVEN_BACK_THEN_HE_WAS_FAMOUS_AMONG_THE                                = 12506,  -- Even back then, he was famous among the students as the sleuth who solved mysteries like the Case of the Vanishing Grimoire and the Case of the Missing Professor.
        AND_YET_THIS_CASE_HAS_EVEN_NICOLAUS_STUMPED                           = 12507,  -- And yet this case has even Nicolaus stumped... I guess that's why I've become so obsessed with it.
        NOW_WHERE_WAS_I_AH_YES_WE_MUST                                        = 12508,  -- Now, where was I...? Ah yes, we must consider the surface area of the floor, and the potential speed of the fleeing assassin...
        WHO_GOES_THERE                                                        = 12509,  -- ...? Who goes there!?
        A_CHILD_THIS_IS_NO_PLACE_FOR_GAMES                                    = 12510,  -- A child? This is no place for games, little one.
        C_C_CAPTAIN_K_K_KLARA                                                 = 12511,  -- C-C-Captain K-K-Klara...!
        I_UM_YOU_SEE_I_M_NOT_HERE                                             = 12512,  -- I, um, you see... I'm not here to play...
        THEN_WHY_ARE_YOU_HERE                                                 = 12513,  -- Then why are you here?
        I_I_I_OH_BOY                                                          = 12514,  -- I-I-I... Oh boy...
        I_CAN_T_BELIEVE_MYTHRIL_MUSKETEER_CAPTAIN_KLARA                       = 12515,  -- (I can't believe Mythril Musketeer Captain Klara is talking to me...!)
        NOT_ABOUT_TO_BREAK_UNDER_INTERROGATION_ARE_WE                         = 12516,  -- Not about to break under interrogation, are we?
        WELL_JUST_SEE_THAT_YOU_DON_T_COME                                     = 12517,  -- Well, just see that you don't come sneaking in here again, okay?
        Y_Y_YES_MA_AM                                                         = 12518,  -- Y-y-yes, ma'am...
        IS_SOMETHING_AMISS_CAPTAIN                                            = 12519,  -- Is something amiss, Captain?
        THAT_CHILD_WAS_POKING_AROUND_IN_CHIEF_ENGINEER                        = 12520,  -- That child was poking around in Chief Engineer Cid's laboratory--the room where Senator Werner was assassinated.
        HE_WHAT_THAT_S_NOT_POSSIBLE                                           = 12521,  -- He what!? That's not possible...
        YES_NO_ONE_HERE_IS_TO_BLAME_NOT                                       = 12522,  -- Yes, no one here is to blame. Not the sentries. Not the guards. No one is at fault...
        I_VE_BEEN_ALERT_THE_ENTIRE_TIME_HOW                                   = 12523,  -- I've been alert the entire time. How did he get in there...?
        THE_PRESIDENT_HAS_RELEASED_A_STATEMENT_REGARDING_SENATOR              = 12524,  -- The president has released a statement regarding Senator Werner's assassination.
        IT_CONTAINED_A_MESSAGE_TO_THE_ASSASSIN_YOU                            = 12525,  -- It contained a message to the assassin: You will not elude the grip of the Mythril Musketeers!
        YOU_WANT_TO_KNOW_HOW_I_SNUCK_INTO                                     = 12526,  -- You want to know how I snuck into the Metalworks?
        THERE_WAS_A_GUARD_AT_THE_ENTRANCE_SO                                  = 12527,  -- There was a guard at the entrance, so I crawled in through the ventilation shaft.
        WHAT_WERE_YOU_THINKING_PAGDAKO                                        = 12528,  -- What were you thinking, Pagdako?
        YOUR_RECKLESSNESS_COULD_HAVE_GOTTEN_YOU_HURT                          = 12529,  -- Your recklessness could have gotten you hurt.
        BUT                                                                   = 12530,  -- But...
        BUT_I_VE_HEARD_SO_MANY_HUMES_SAYING                                   = 12531,  -- But I've heard so many Humes saying that maybe Elder Werei and Gumbah were responsible for the Senator's death!
        I_THOUGHT_IF_I_COULD_FIND_THE_REAL                                    = 12532,  -- I thought if I could find the real culprit, their names would be cleared.
        IS_THAT_WHAT_THEY_RE_SAYING_THOSE_HUMES                               = 12533,  -- Is that what they're saying? Those Humes will take any opportunity to drag us down...!
        I_LL_ADMIT_THERE_MAY_BE_A_FEW                                         = 12534,  -- I'll admit, there may be a few individuals among the Galkan community that didn't shed a tear at the senator's death. But that doesn't mean we'd stoop to murder.
        AND_I_M_ASHAMED_AS_A_FELLOW_BASTOKAN                                  = 12535,  -- And I'm ashamed as a fellow Bastokan that any would accuse your elders of such.
        ELDER_WEREI                                                           = 12536,  -- Elder Werei!
