        HEY_HAVE_YOU_HEARD_SOME_QUADAVS_HAVE_BEGUN                            = 12759,  -- Hey, have you heard? Some Quadavs have begun equipping a new type of armor that has our army completely baffled.
        IT_S_SUPPOSED_TO_BE_BULLETPROOF_IF_THIS                               = 12760,  -- It's supposed to be bulletproof. If this new armor were to be mass produced by the Quadav, we'd be in quite a tight spot. The issue's been causing mayhem in the Allied War Council.
